data.description: Located only minutes from the BEACH and a few feet from Kitty Hawk BAY, this well-maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bath home offers an excellent investment opportunity, as a vacation home or a primary residence. Upon entering the home, you will be blown away by the wood floors and vaulted ceilings creating a spacious and open ambience to this charming home. The kitchen is open and inviting, and it boasts an eat-dining area situated in front of bay windows. Additionally, the first floor features a primary bedroom for added convenience and privacy. On the second floor, you'll find two large rooms that can be utilized as additional bedrooms, a home office, or guest rooms. The back patio is a great place for entertaining or for enjoying evenings by a fire listening to the “working” coy pond. This home’s convenient location gives easy access to shopping, dining and other amenities and attractions in the area. Seller shall provide a home warranty not to exceed $700, at closing.
